Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.38,0:02:52.16,Default,Narrator,0,0,0,,All the pirates vying for the One Piece\Nhead for the second half of the Grand Line.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.16,0:02:54.69,Default,Narrator,0,0,0,,People call it the "New World."
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.08,0:03:03.43,Default,Narrator,0,0,0,,However, the only one to ever conquer\Nthese waters was the Pirate King, Gold Roger.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.64,0:03:09.74,Default,Narrator,0,0,0,,The New World has ruined\Nmany pirates' dreams and ambitions.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.50,0:03:16.11,Default,Narrator,0,0,0,,Now, the boy whose body turned to rubber\Nafter eating the Gum-Gum Fruit,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.11,0:03:19.38,Default,Narrator,0,0,0,,Monkey D. Luffy and his crew\Nventure into that very sea.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.09,0:03:23.52,Default,Luffy,0,0,0,,I'm gonna be the Pirate King!!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.36,0:03:28.93,Default,,0,0,0,,On their way to the New World,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.93,0:03:33.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Luffy and his crew reached Fishman Island located 10,000 meters below sea level,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.30,0:03:38.80,Default,,0,0,0,,where the New Fishman Pirates who are looking to destroy the Ryugu Kingdom...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.80,0:03:42.54,Default,,0,0,0,,...assisted by Vander Decken, who is after Shirahoshi, are engaging in secret maneuvers.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.54,0:03:48.01,Default,,0,0,0,,The Straw Hats find themselves caught up in the turmoil and involved in an all-out war.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.01,0:03:53.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, Hody's merciless plot puts Fishman Island in unprecedented danger!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.79,0:04:00.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Weren't you listening to what I said?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.43,0:04:04.53,Default,,0,0,0,,I will save Fishman Island and Shirahoshi...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.33,0:04:07.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Luffy-sama...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.00,0:04:09.37,Default,,0,0,0,,...and keep my promise to a friend.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.87,0:04:11.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Straw Hat...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.30,0:04:14.57,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll protect...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.57,0:04:16.31,Default,,0,0,0,,...everything!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.31,0:04:20.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Scoring Song: Blizzard Slice!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.01,0:04:22.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Impact Wolf!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.18,0:04:25.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Hoofprint: Palme!
