Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.75,0:04:29.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Squid! Squid! Squid!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.49,0:04:32.46,Default,,0,0,0,,...Radical Beam!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.69,0:04:36.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Vagabond Drill!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.33,0:04:38.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Hell Memories!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.56,0:04:41.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Purgatory...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.03,0:04:43.67,Default,,0,0,0,,...Demon Slash!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.67,0:04:45.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Gum-Gum...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.90,0:04:49.04,Default,,0,0,0,,...Elephant Gun!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.04,0:04:53.58,Default,,0,0,0,,I will stop the Noah!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.58,0:04:57.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Keep falling, Noah!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.32,0:05:05.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Kill all the pride-less Fishmen!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.63,0:05:20.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Gum-Gum...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.17,0:05:25.34,Default,,0,0,0,,...Elephant Gatling!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.41,0:05:34.38,B1,,0,0,0,,{\fad(2000,2000)}"Stop, Noah! Desperate Elephant Gatling!"
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.57,0:06:01.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Even those demon-like officers are a joke to them. That's how strong they are!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.74,0:06:35.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Stay alert!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.75,0:06:38.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Look up! You're in danger!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.92,0:06:40.18,Default,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.69,0:06:46.56,Default,,0,0,0,,--Wadatsumi is... --...Falling toward us!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.44,0:07:03.11,Default,,0,0,0,,You should've dropped him elsewhere, you worthless chef!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.11,0:07:06.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Shut up! I'll make someone fall onto you next time!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.45,0:07:16.32,Default,,0,0,0,,That was amazing, Sanji.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.26,0:07:22.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey Chopper! Could you shrink yourself a little bit?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.53,0:07:25.40,Default,,0,0,0,,You're upstaging the giant robot!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.40,0:07:28.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Franky, I loved the beam!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.50,0:07:31.94,Default,,0,0,0,,That robot was totally useless.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.91,0:07:36.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh! Nami-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.91,0:07:38.08,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.94,0:07:40.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Please wear a miniskirt.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.68,0:07:41.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Shut up!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.18,0:07:50.22,Default,,0,0,0,,That's just what I'd expect from Luffy-kun's friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.97,0:08:04.84,Default,,0,0,0,,He did it!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.81,0:08:16.91,Default,,0,0,0,,This time for sure! Luffy-san beat Hody!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.05,0:08:21.28,Default,,0,0,0,,--Did you hear that? --Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.59,0:08:36.30,Default,,0,0,0,,The Straw Hats defeated the New Fishman Pirates!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.04,0:08:45.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.74,0:08:47.51,Default,,0,0,0,,The Noah!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.62,0:09:00.16,Default,,0,0,0,,The Noah is right there!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.56,0:09:07.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Run!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.00,0:09:10.27,Default,,0,0,0,,It's gonna destroy us along with the island!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.27,0:09:14.44,Default,,0,0,0,,If we stay here any longer, Neptune's army will bar us in the plaza!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.44,0:09:17.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Hurry up! Those crazy officers are gone now!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.34,0:09:23.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh my goodness! How is the evacuation going?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.71,0:09:26.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Only a few citizens have escaped to the sea.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.32,0:09:31.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Most people are still here on the island!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.20,0:09:41.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.60,0:09:45.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Is it too late?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.14,0:09:52.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Can't you do anything, Straw Hat?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.81,0:09:55.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Straw Hat!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.65,0:10:02.05,Default,,0,0,0,,The threat of rebellion is now gone but...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.46,0:10:06.39,Default,,0,0,0,,This is it!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.39,0:10:07.96,Default,,0,0,0,,No, not yet!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.96,0:10:09.23,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.93,0:10:15.90,Default,,0,0,0,,He is not...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.34,0:10:20.97,Default,,0,0,0,,...giving up yet!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.67,0:10:27.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Straw Hat Luffy-san is...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.82,0:10:34.52,Default,,0,0,0,,...trying his best...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.79,0:10:38.76,Default,,0,0,0,,...to destroy...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.59,0:10:42.19,Default,,0,0,0,,...the Noah!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.41,0:11:00.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Destroy the Noah?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.88,0:11:02.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Trying to destroy it?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.55,0:11:05.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Destroy that giant ship?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.42,0:11:08.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Really?! That's impossible!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.45,0:11:11.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Prepare for the worst, guys!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.29,0:11:13.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah. Let's just stand by him.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.33,0:11:18.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Luffy-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.21,0:11:32.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Luffy-sama!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.75,0:11:41.45,Default,,0,0,0,,If he can destroy the Noah before it hits the island, we'll be okay but...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.45,0:11:44.29,Default,,0,0,0,,...if he can't,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.29,0:11:48.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Fishman Island will fall!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.63,0:11:51.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Give it everything you got, Luffy!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.40,0:11:55.57,Default,,0,0,0,,--Luffy-san! --We're counting on you, Luffy!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.57,0:11:58.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Luffy!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.77,0:12:01.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Luffy-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.78,0:12:08.38,Default,,0,0,0,,What's wrong?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.38,0:12:10.61,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not gonna run!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.61,0:12:13.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't be ridiculous! Can't you see the Noah?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.48,0:12:16.52,Default,,0,0,0,,I know! I know, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.52,0:12:21.12,Default,,0,0,0,,...Straw Hat's heroic actions bring back memories of...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.12,0:12:24.56,Default,,0,0,0,,...what happened 20 years ago when I was a kid!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.83,0:12:32.97,Default,,0,0,0,,There was one human that the people of this kingdom thanked with all our hearts!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.41,0:12:42.85,Default,,0,0,0,,What a haul!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.55,0:12:44.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.45,0:12:45.45,Default,,0,0,0,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.79,0:12:51.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Who are you?! Do you wanna die?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.32,0:12:56.86,Default,,0,0,0,,You got to be kidding me! Why is he...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.50,0:13:01.03,Default,,0,0,0,,...taking the Fishmen's side?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.87,0:13:06.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Neptune helped me when we were young and we exchanged
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.64,0:13:09.34,Default,,0,0,0,,cups of sake as a pledge of friendship!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.84,0:13:16.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't kill me! I promise I'll never kidnap Mermaids and Fishmen!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.65,0:13:22.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't mess with my friend's country!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.19,0:13:25.29,Default,,0,0,0,,You wet-nosed brats!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.46,0:13:36.67,Default,,0,0,0,,I declare that this island is my territory now!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.84,0:13:43.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you talking about Whitebeard?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.01,0:13:47.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you saying you trust them like you trusted the great pirate?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.34,0:13:48.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Because,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.48,0:13:51.95,Default,,0,0,0,,to be honest, I don't even like humans
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.95,0:13:54.08,Default,,0,0,0,,and this is the Fishmen's kingdom,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.55,0:13:55.49,Default,,0,0,0,,but they...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.09,0:14:00.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Our minds were made up when we arrived at the plaza that,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.56,0:14:03.86,Default,,0,0,0,,along with Jinbe, we wouldn't let anyone harm the island!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.29,0:14:06.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Leave it all up to us, Brother-hoshi!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.10,0:14:08.90,Default,,0,0,0,,We're friends, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.23,0:14:13.77,Default,,0,0,0,,He said such things and they're all risking their lives...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.99,0:14:33.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Straw Hat...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.62,0:15:06.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't lose, Straw Hat!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.16,0:15:09.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, Straw Hat, we're supporting you!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.16,0:15:11.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Hang in there, Straw Hat!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.26,0:15:16.27,Default,,0,0,0,,--You're a human and you're fighting for us! --We're not gonna run!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.77,0:15:20.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Go, Big Bro Straw Hat!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.28,0:15:32.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Please save Fishman Island, Straw Hat!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.65,0:15:34.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Go, Straw Hat!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.98,0:15:37.15,Default,,0,0,0,,We believe in you!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.69,0:15:39.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Straw Hat!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.86,0:15:41.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Straw Hat!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.86,0:15:44.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Straw Hat!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.60,0:15:47.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Luffy-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.34,0:15:55.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Straw Hat!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.00,0:15:56.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Straw Hat!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.77,0:15:58.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Straw Hat!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.74,0:16:00.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Straw Hat!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.88,0:16:02.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Straw Hat!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.18,0:16:05.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Straw Hat!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.05,0:16:07.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Straw Hat!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.32,0:16:09.72,Default,,0,0,0,,--Straw Hat! --Straw Hat!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.72,0:16:11.89,Default,,0,0,0,,--Straw Hat! --Straw Hat!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.89,0:16:15.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop, Noah!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.09,0:16:16.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.93,0:16:19.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.54,0:16:30.84,Default,,0,0,0,,I only broke half of it so far!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.11,0:16:37.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Luffy-sama!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.12,0:16:42.99,Default,,0,0,0,,The wound is opening up...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.99,0:16:44.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Stay away!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.12,0:16:48.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Stay there and watch!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.16,0:16:51.29,Default,,0,0,0,,I need to keep destroying this thing now!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.13,0:16:59.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop, ship!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.54,0:17:05.21,Default,,0,0,0,,--Straw Hat! --Straw Hat!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.21,0:17:08.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Luffy, go for it!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.08,0:17:10.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Break it into pieces!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.25,0:17:12.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Super!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.33,0:17:27.30,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry, Father.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.30,0:17:31.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Destroying the Noah is the only way.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.77,0:17:33.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Straw Hat!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.04,0:17:35.91,Default,,0,0,0,,The Ship of Promise...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.47,0:17:37.84,Default,,0,0,0,,But it cannot be helped.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.84,0:17:39.64,Default,,0,0,0,,People's lives are the most important.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.21,0:17:44.55,Default,,0,0,0,,I am sorry. I cannot keep the promise-jamon,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.55,0:17:46.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Joyboy!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.39,0:18:00.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Just a little more to go!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.97,0:18:07.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Please...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.34,0:18:15.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.92,0:18:28.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Who is it?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.96,0:18:35.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Luffy-sama! Please stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.87,0:18:39.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Luffy-sama, you have to stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.74,0:18:44.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Move, Wimpyhoshi! I need to destroy it to save the island!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.81,0:18:48.64,Default,,0,0,0,,It's okay now!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.64,0:18:52.05,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not okay! Everybody's on the island!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.05,0:18:53.45,Default,,0,0,0,,The Noah is already...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.78,0:18:56.89,Default,,0,0,0,,...stopped!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.90,0:19:09.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Sea Kings? Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.34,0:19:17.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Luffy-sama is angry!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.41,0:19:19.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, this is no time for crying!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.85,0:19:28.82,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't quite understand, either.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.92,0:19:34.26,Default,,0,0,0,,But the Noah is stopped now!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.89,0:19:39.50,Default,,0,0,0,,What happened?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.50,0:19:43.47,Default,,0,0,0,,What's going on here? The Sea Kings stopped the ship!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.64,0:19:53.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Luffy-sama! The wound is opening up again!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.41,0:19:55.65,Default,,0,0,0,,You are bleeding a lot!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.12,0:20:02.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Well... Well... That's good...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.82,0:20:07.49,Default,,0,0,0,,...as long as the ship is stopped.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.59,0:20:12.53,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm glad everybody's...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.53,0:20:14.20,Default,,0,0,0,,...safe.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.50,0:20:17.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Luffy-sama!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.04,0:20:20.70,Default,,0,0,0,,He's fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.61,0:20:33.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Boy, what a human!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.65,0:20:37.49,Default,,0,0,0,,He is a very strong one, isn't he?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.49,0:20:41.79,Default,,0,0,0,,If we were late, we could still have saved the island
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.79,0:20:45.53,Default,,0,0,0,,but the Noah would have been completely destroyed.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.43,0:20:51.27,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm glad that we made it!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.27,0:20:56.44,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm glad that Princess Shirahoshi called us!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.44,0:21:01.38,Default,,0,0,0,,What? I didn't do anything and I was just sad...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.38,0:21:07.88,Default,,0,0,0,,No, you were moved by Straw Hat boy's strong determination
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.88,0:21:09.95,Default,,0,0,0,,and prayed.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.36,0:21:22.50,Default,,0,0,0,,You wished strongly to help him save the island.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.71,0:21:41.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Our power is your power.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.78,0:21:46.29,Default,,0,0,0,,We helped him because you called us.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.71,0:22:06.38,Default,,0,0,0,,A-All people of the kingdom.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.38,0:22:12.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Wh-What just happened here was beyond words
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.05,0:22:15.52,Default,,0,0,0,,but it happened for sure!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.12,0:22:18.42,Default,,0,0,0,,The Noah is stopped!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.86,0:22:25.73,Default,,0,0,0,,The ship didn't get destroyed completely
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.33,0:22:30.87,Default,,0,0,0,,and Fishman Island has been saved!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.47,0:22:35.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Straw Hat did it!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.81,0:22:40.11,Default,,0,0,0,,--Straw Hat! --So we're safe, aren't we?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.11,0:22:41.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.95,0:22:45.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Straw Hat!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.38,0:22:47.48,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm so relieved!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.15,0:22:53.09,Default,,0,0,0,,--Yeah! --Oh, he did it!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.09,0:22:58.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Luffy did it!!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.91,0:23:20.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Fishman Island is saved.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.32,0:23:23.29,Default,,0,0,0,,However, in his fight to achieve this...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.29,0:23:26.32,Default,,0,0,0,,...Luffy is in critical condition with a multitude of wounds.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.32,0:23:30.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Yet the Fishmen, still bound by the island's past...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.03,0:23:32.36,Default,,0,0,0,,...hesitate to come to his aid.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.36,0:23:34.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Just when Luffy is almost out of time...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.90,0:23:38.37,Default,,0,0,0,,...a single man's actions alter the course of history.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.37,0:23:39.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Next time, on One Piece:
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.97,0:23:42.47,Default,,0,0,0,,"The Secret Revealed! The Truth about the Ancient Weapon!"
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.47,0:23:44.67,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm gonna be the Pirate King!!
